claim.claim-text:
1. An interface definition comprising;
an electrical signal set definition, wherein the electrical signal set definition comprises a plurality of dual port USB (DPUSB) signals, one reserved signal, a write protect signal and a card detect signal and wherein the plurality of DPSUB signals comprises peripheral differential data lines and host differential data lines;
a mechanical and electrical definition for a memory card;
an associated memory card signal and mechanical specification for a memory card; and
a mechanical definition for cables compatible with an interface socket.
